OL,3,CCommunity gathers for vigil after
OL,4,CBallymena tragedy
OL,6,FA vigil is to take place in
OL,7,Fremembrance of the victims of an
OL,8,Fattack in Ballymena that saw three
OL,9,Fpeople killed, including an eight-year-
OL,10,Fold girl.
OL,12,FThe PSNI has said the three were from
OL,13,Fthe same family, and were a 41-year-
OL,14,Fold man, a 39-year-old woman and the
OL,15,Fyoung girl.
OL,17,FThe adults are believed to have
OL,18,Foriginally been from Poland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
