OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784308722
OL,3,CCommunity gathers for vigil after
OL,4,CBallymena tragedy
OL,6,FPolice investigators' "strong
OL,7,Fhypothesis" is that the incident was a
OL,8,Fdouble murder followed by a sudden
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FFlowers were left at the house by
OL,12,Fneighbours, as the community is left
OL,13,Fin shock after the three bodies were
OL,14,Fdiscovered at the property in the Old
OL,15,FCullybackey Road area on Monday.
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,18,Fsaid he was "deeply saddened to hear
OL,19,Fthe news of the terrible tragedy".
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@KO]zD@MOU{D@aO]
