OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784308722
OL,3,CCommunity gathers for vigil after
OL,4,CBallymena tragedy
OL,6,FHe posted on X: "My thoughts are with
OL,7,Fthe victims, their loved ones and the
OL,8,Flocal community at this very difficult
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,F"I urge anyone with any information at
OL,12,Fall to contact the PSNI."
OL,14,FThe vigil is to take place on
OL,15,FWednesday evening outside The Braid
OL,16,FArts Centre in the centre of Ballymena.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUtD@YO]
