PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784308722
OL,3,CCommunity gathers for vigil after
OL,4,CBallymena tragedy
OL,6,FThe organisers of the event, Youth
OL,7,FAmbassadors Northern Ireland, wrote in
OL,8,Fa social media post that was also
OL,9,Ftranslated into Polish: "In light of
OL,10,Fthe recent tragedy in Ballymena we
OL,11,Finvite all members of our community
OL,12,Fboth near and far to join us for a
OL,13,Fmoment of quiet reflection, light and
OL,14,Funity.
OL,16,F"We stand with all those affected,
OL,17,Fespecially the local Polish community,
OL,18,Fduring this difficult time."
